Hi Daniel,

There is no support for this monitor yet, but there will be no problem
to add support for it, as the same model, but with 17" screen size, is
supported (760BF).

So if you buy it, please send the output of "LANG= LC_ALL= ddccontrol -p
-c -d" to this list, and support will be added in the following days.

Best regards,

Nicolas

